\par }\pard \li180 {\f2 Please compose your articles thoughtfully.  Consider sending an }{\f2\ul electronic mail message}{\v\f2 electronic_mail_message}{\f2  rather than posting an article, if appropriate.  
\par 
\par Be aware of the fact that many sites must pay long-distance telephone charges to receive your article.  Also be aware of the fact that some of the popular newsgroups have tens of thousands of readers.  10,000 people each reading your article for 20 second
s spend a total of 55 hours reading your article.
