\par In order to keep track of your viewing history, WinVN records information about }{\f2\ul newsgroups}{\v\f2 newsgroup}{\f2  in a file named NEWSRC.  This file contains a list of all newsgroups.  For each newsgroup, WinVN records whether it is subscribed an
d which articles have been seen.
\par 
\par Many Unix-based }{\f2\ul news readers}{\v\f2 news_reader}{\f2  record this information in a file named }{\b\f2 .newsrc}{\f2 .  WinVN uses the same file format to provide compatibility with these programs.
\par 
