\par WinVN offers a number of configuration options.  All are accessible from the }{\b\f2 Options}{\f2  menu of the }{\f2\uldb main window}{\v\f2 main_window}{\f2 .  The }{\b\f2 Configure Comm...}{\f2  option allows you to set communications parameters.  These
 parameters must be set properly for WinVN to work.
\par 
\par The }{\b\f2 Configure Personal Info...}{\f2  and }{\b\f2 Configure Miscellaneous...}{\f2  options allow you to specify information about yourself and to set WinVN preferences.  This information is not vital to the proper operation of WinVN.
